(988,174,"about_us_main_text_area","We have 40 plus years of combined automotive repair experience employing quality ASE certified master technicians equipped with the latest technology and diagnostic tools to service all foreign and domestic cars and light trucks. Our staff of professionals are dedicated to making your auto repair experience the best ever.\r\n\r\nVan Handel Automotive was established in March of 2007. Formerly Sisters Car Care, this location has serviced the community of Sisters and the surrounding area for many years. We have given the shop a face lift and a new attitude.\r\n\r\nWe understand that your vehicle is a major investment. That is why we care for each customers vehicle as if it was our own. Come by and visit our clean and professional shop in Sisters, Oregon."),
